refentry.refsect1:
&reftitle.parameters;




   rarfile



     A RarArchive object, opened with rar_open.

&reftitle.changelog;







     &Version;
     &Description;





     2.0.0

      The RAR entries returned by RarArchive::getEntry
      and RarArchive::list are now invalidated when
      calling this method. This means that all instance methods called for
      such entries and not guaranteed to succeed.

  &reftitle.examples;



    Object oriented style


<?php
$rar_arch = RarArchive::open('latest_winrar.rar');
echo $rar_arch."\n";
$rar_arch->close();
echo $rar_arch."\n";
?>


     &example.outputs.similar;


RAR Archive "D:\php_rar\trunk\tests\latest_winrar.rar"
RAR Archive "D:\php_rar\trunk\tests\latest_winrar.rar" (closed)







    Procedural style


<?php
$rar_arch = rar_open('latest_winrar.rar');
echo $rar_arch."\n";
rar_close($rar_arch);
echo $rar_arch."\n";
?>
